Bloom::Filter version 0.01
===================

A pure-perl implementation of Bloom filters.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Digest::SHA1

